'''Auriga''' can refer to:*Auriga (constellation), a constellation of stars*Auriga (slave), a Roman slave chauffeur*HMS Auriga (P419), a British submarine launched in 1945*"Auriga of Delphi", name of the statue "Charioteer of Delphi"*USM ''Auriga'', a spaceship in the film ''Alien Resurrection''*Auriga (company), a software R;D and IT outsourcing services provider